Package: regtools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for presenting regressions results
Version: 0.1
Date: 2014-08-14
Author: Sebastian Kranz
Maintainer: Sebastian Kranz <sebastian.kranz@uni-ulm.de>
Description: Mainly, shall make it easier to present regression results like in
    economics articles. E.g. easy inclusion of robust standard errors and marginal
    effects. Consists mostly of wrapper and glue functions to texreg, sandwich, mfx
    etc. Not yet thoroghly tested.
License: GPL>=2.0
Depends:
    restorepoint,
    sandwich,
    mvtnorm,
    dplyr
Imports:
    mfx,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr,
    texreg,
    stargazer
RoxygenNote: 5.0.0
